&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;isPasted&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Five Rings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;isPasted&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Five Rings is a proprietary trading firm founded with a vision of combining strategy, innovation and technology to succeed in today’s global markets. With offices in New York, Boca Raton, London and Amsterdam, Five Rings trades in various domestic and international markets, both established and esoteric. Our team constantly seeks new opportunities, analyzes their risks and rewards, and creates strategies and tools to capitalize on them.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We have an open culture and encourage the flow of knowledge and ideas between all areas of the firm.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;New York based 200-person trading firm seeks a Trading Operations Engineer to provide technical operations support for US and UK based desks.&amp;nbsp; This individual is part of the firm’s Technology division but sits on the trading desk and is embedded in the technical operations processes of the firm.&amp;nbsp; The task set is roughly split evenly between desk facing activities and light coding tasks often in collaboration with full time development staff.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Duties and responsibilities include but are not limited to:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; • First point of contact for traders utilizing the firm’s trading systems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; • Install, configure and monitor critical trading applications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; • Incident management via ticketing system and documentation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; • Collaborate with developers for all operational processes supporting trading applications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Required skills:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; • Strong problem solving and multitasking abilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; • Experience with Python, bash and MySQL on Linux is required&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; • Excellent communication skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;em&gt;Applicants are able to apply to multiple positions, but we strongly encourage you to only apply to your top choice.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Range reflects annual base salary. Total compensation packages are comprised of base salary and a discretionary bonus.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;isPasted&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Five Rings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;isPasted&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Five Rings is a proprietary trading firm founded with a vision of combining strategy, innovation and technology to succeed in today’s global markets. With offices in New York, Boca Raton, London and Amsterdam, Five Rings trades in various domestic and international markets, both established and esoteric. Our team constantly seeks new opportunities, analyzes their risks and rewards, and creates strategies and tools to capitalize on them.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We have an open culture and encourage the flow of knowledge and ideas between all areas of the firm.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our New York office is seeking to employ a Trading Assistant. This individual will be responsible for manually inputting and updating orders for constantly changing markets throughout trading hours, coordinating with traders to deliver relevant and correct information, and consistently monitoring the state of the market. They must also be capable and comfortable working and communicating accurately in a time-sensitive environment and have the ability to multitask by prioritizing the input of key market data first. Lastly, they must be able to reconcile trades daily with accuracy and precision by checking trade records against our internal records.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note this role is 100% in-office 5 days per week and responsibilities are aligned with market hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will possess a bachelor’s degree, be a self-starter, an excellent communicator, and be able to execute quickly in a time-sensitive environment. Exceptional attention to detail, organizational skills, and ability to multitask are all essential for success in this role.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Range reflects annual base salary. Total compensation packages are comprised of base salary and a discretionary bonus.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Salary Range:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$100,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$100,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;isPasted&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Five Rings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
