&lt;p&gt;A dynamic NYC-based trading firm is looking for a Compliance Analyst to join its growing compliance&amp;nbsp; team. The team is charged with establishing, implementing and maintaining adequate policies and&amp;nbsp; procedures to ensure compliance of the firm with its legal and regulatory obligations. In this position,&amp;nbsp; tasks will primarily include surveillance and monitoring of trading activity, training and inducting staff,&amp;nbsp; documenting new policies, managing regulatory reporting and communication, administering existing&amp;nbsp; policies, and monitoring regulatory developments and best practices.&lt;/p&gt;
